In [196]:
# changes made in the sub_set of "a" can change the the original
print("Shows that change in the sub array changes the original list:")
sub_set = a[:2,1:3]
sub_set[0,0] = 60
print(sub_set[0,0])
print(a[0,1])
# Inorder to prevent this we use ".copy()"
print("shows how to prevent the above:")
sub_setb = a[:2, 1:13].copy()
sub_setb[0,0] = 50
print(sub_setb[0,0])
print(a[0,1])
